    <name>Presentation: A Strategy for Teaching Summarization [Video]</name>
    <intro>&lt;p&gt;Writing a summary is a key research-based activity that supports both writing development and reading comprehension. Learning to do it well will benefit adult students as they progress in content area learning in post-secondary and career and technical education.&lt;/p&gt;</intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
